<text id="02-output-contract" title="Rails Decomposition Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the structural-lint manifest this methodology produces. Validator enforces required keys + per-field constraints.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/decomposition-rails.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["ruby_version", "rails_version", "services", "query_objects", "form_objects", "namespace_whitelist_passed", "file_size_budgets"],
  "properties": {
    "ruby_version": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^3\\."},
    "rails_version": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^(7|8)\\."},
    "services": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["class", "returns"],
        "properties": {
          "class": {"type": "string", "pattern": "Service$"},
          "returns": {"type": "string", "not": {"enum": ["void", "nil"]}}
        }
      }
    },
    "query_objects": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["class", "reuses_scopes"],
        "properties": {
          "class": {"type": "string", "pattern": "Query$"},
          "reuses_scopes": {"type": "boolean", "const": true}
        }
      }
    },
    "form_objects": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["class", "base"],
        "properties": {
          "class": {"type": "string", "pattern": "Form$"},
          "base": {"const": "ActiveModel::Model"}
        }
      }
    },
    "namespace_whitelist_passed": {"type": "boolean", "const": true},
    "file_size_budgets": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["service_max", "controller_max"],
      "properties": {
        "service_max": {"type": "integer", "maximum": 100},
        "controller_max": {"type": "integer", "maximum": 150}
      }
    },
    "forbidden_patterns_found": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}, "maxItems": 0}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "ruby_version": "3.3",
  "rails_version": "7.1",
  "services": [{"class": "Users::CreateService", "returns": "User"}],
  "query_objects": [{"class": "Users::ActiveUsersQuery", "reuses_scopes": true}],
  "form_objects": [{"class": "Users::SignupForm", "base": "ActiveModel::Model"}],
  "namespace_whitelist_passed": true,
  "file_size_budgets": {"service_max": 88, "controller_max": 132},
  "forbidden_patterns_found": []
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "ruby_version": "2.7",
  "rails_version": "6.0",
  "services": [{"class": "UserManager", "returns": "void"}],
  "query_objects": [{"class": "ActiveUsers", "reuses_scopes": false}],
  "form_objects": [{"class": "SignupForm", "base": "ActiveRecord::Base"}],
  "namespace_whitelist_passed": false,
  "file_size_budgets": {"service_max": 320, "controller_max": 480},
  "forbidden_patterns_found": ["app/managers/ namespace not on whitelist"]
}
]]></code>
    <note>Ruby + Rails versions out of range; Service named UserManager, returns void; query re-implements scopes; form inherits AR; whitelist fail.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>Service class name not suffixed with `Service`.</item>
      <item>`def call; ...; end` returning `nil` or `void` semantics.</item>
      <item>Form Object inheriting from `ActiveRecord::Base` or `ActiveType::Object`.</item>
      <item>Serializer using `attributes :all` / `model.as_json` without explicit list.</item>
      <item>Controller calling `Model.find` without `policy_scope`.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-decomposition-rails.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
